                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18021201-16-defend164 t18021201-16-punish92"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Grose.</p>
